data.actual_result: Nothing happens and you are still muted, and cant speak.
data.expected_result: You can unmute youre mic, and you can speak in the call.
data.short_description: I cant unmute my mic in DM Group Calls
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to a DM Group and click on "start call" - Click on the notification bar of your mobil device on the mute button, or use the Discord Call Overview bar in the Discord App and click on the Mute Button
